| **URL** | [dawncreative.co.uk](https://www.dawncreative.co.uk/) |
| --- | --- |
| **Type** | Brand, Digital and Motion agency, Manchester — Certified B Corp |
| **Clients** | Adidas (global event content), Softbank, Rick Shiels Media, Zen Internet, Calla Shoes, Disabled Living |
| **Hero Headline** | “Your brand is a sleeping giant. Let’s wake it up.” (rotating through Brand / Digital / Motion) |
| **Secondary Headline** | “We move brands forward. Faster, smarter, and with purpose. No fluff. No delay. Just clear thinking, bold ideas, and continual improvement.” |
| **Positioning Statement** | “We are Dawn. A Certified B Corp™, brand-first creative agency hell-bent on helping you shine.” |
| **Page Structure** | Hero (rotating service focus) → service menu → project showcase (looping videos) → service descriptions → testimonials carousel → client logos → editorial blog → contact |
| **Primary CTA** | “Get in touch” in navigation. “Connect with us” in footer. Phone and email prominent. |
