| **What makes it exceptional** | The combination of an opinionated, warm headline with strong testimonials and clear service descriptions creates a page that feels both aspirational and accessible. The B Corp certification signals values alignment — increasingly important for purpose-driven clients. The blog/editorial content strengthens SEO and authority simultaneously. |
