| **Key lesson for Image Foundry** | “No fluff. No delay.” is a promise about working style that resonates with busy marketing managers and developers. Consider weaving a similar operational promise into the Image Foundry landing page — something about how the studio actually works: turnaround, communication, responsiveness. |

